title: Kodak Black Is Going To Be A Father
text:
Home > Music > Kodak Black Is Going To Be A Father Kodak Black Is Going To Be A Father 0 0 Posted  24pm Kodak Black is going to be a dad. 
It looks like Kodak Black ’s pull out game aint the strongest. On Friday, the Florida rapper took to his IG to announce that he’s going to be a father. 
With a picture of the ultrasound, Kodak left the caption: “I Done Fucked Round N Got A Bih Pregnant , My Lawyer Hollin Nigga Pay Me #WordsCantExplain ." It's unknown if the baby mama is a girlfriend or random woman, but either way it should definitely change Kodak's life for the better. 
This announcement comes on the heels of his much-talked about video for "Everything 1K," which features "cash me ousside" internet sensation Danielle Bregoli. A photo posted by Project Baby (@kodakblack) on Feb 10, 2017 at 5:16pm PST < class="robots-nocontent" rel=""> Feb 10, 2017 at 09:24pm 1 View
